      <title>ReZero从零开始搭建前后端项目（一）</title>
      <link href="/2022/02/17/rezero-cong-ling-kai-shi-da-jian-qian-hou-duan-xiang-mu-yi/"/>
      <url>/2022/02/17/rezero-cong-ling-kai-shi-da-jian-qian-hou-duan-xiang-mu-yi/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><p>layout: rezero<br>title: 从零开始搭建前后端项目（一）<br>date: 2022-02-17 15:56:20<br>tags:</p><hr><h2 id="搭建后端项目"><a href="#搭建后端项目" class="headerlink" title="搭建后端项目"></a>搭建后端项目</h2><blockquote><p>工具 IntelliJ IDEA Community Edition 2020.3</p></blockquote><h4 id="springboot-基础项目"><a href="#springboot-基础项目" class="headerlink" title="springboot 基础项目"></a>springboot 基础项目</h4><p><img src="/.io//1.png" alt="创建新的maven项目.png">  </p><p><img src="/.io//2.png" alt="定义项目基本信息.png"></p><blockquote><p>项目创建结束 打开初始化的pom 文件添加必要的springboot依赖</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!--添加 spring boot 依赖--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;parent&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-parent&lt;/artifactId&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;version&gt;2.2.6.RELEASE&lt;/version&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/parent&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    &lt;dependencies&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;!--该依赖包含spring-boot-starter,还自动开启了web功能 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;dependency&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-web&lt;/artifactId&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/dependency&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;dependency&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-test&lt;/artifactId&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;scope&gt;test&lt;/scope&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/dependency&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/dependencies&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>添加项目启动类 此时添加完成便可启动项目（目录一般以与网站相反的顺序命名 如showcase.ankicoo.com 包名一般为 com.ankicoo.showcase） </p></blockquote><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/19390595-d12e15722975e3ce.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/800" alt="基础启动类.png"></p><blockquote><p>添加配置文件 resources 目录下添加application.yml 或者 application.yaml文件 区别于语法 可自行了解此处使用的是.yaml 文件</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/19390595-9a5dac26f324b78b.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="配置文件.png"></p><blockquote><p>启动项目可见下图提示 项目启动于配置的8080端口 且服务内容在端口下的 /showcase 路径</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/19390595-4c6c3797a0a54a16.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/800" alt="启动信息.png"></p><blockquote><p>添加接口层 用于返回数据</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/19390595-48e6e1070de1eb62.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/800" alt="接口信息.png"></p><blockquote><p>前端访问服务器启动端口 加上context-path 加上路径 便可获得返回内容 本地启动服务 可从 localhost 或127.0.0.1 查看 如 <a href="http://127.0.0.1:8080/showcase/display/hello">http://127.0.0.1:8080/showcase/display/hello</a></p></blockquote><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/19390595-01cd04cd8b286837.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="访问接口.png"></p><h4 id="添加数据库操作"><a href="#添加数据库操作" class="headerlink" title="添加数据库操作"></a>添加数据库操作</h4><blockquote><p>添加用于访问数据库的依赖，此处使用mysql数据库 使用 tk.mybatis 用于访问数据获取数据 添加下列依赖 版本可按需更改</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!--Mysql--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;dependency&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;groupId&gt;mysql&lt;/groupId&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;artifactId&gt;mysql-connector-java&lt;/artifactId&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;version&gt;8.0.16&lt;/version&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/dependency&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!--mybatis--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;dependency&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;groupId&gt;org.mybatis.spring.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;artifactId&gt;mybatis-spring-boot-starter&lt;/artifactId&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;version&gt;1.3.2&lt;/version&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/dependency&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        &lt;!--tk.mybatis mapper--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;dependency&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;groupId&gt;tk.mybatis&lt;/groupId&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;artifactId&gt;mapper&lt;/artifactId&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;version&gt;4.0.4&lt;/version&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/dependency&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;dependency&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;groupId&gt;tk.mybatis&lt;/groupId&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;artifactId&gt;mapper-spring-boot-starter&lt;/artifactId&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;version&gt;2.0.4&lt;/version&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/dependency&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>添加数据库配置 于application.yaml文件中</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/19390595-5a43a8a5508f813f.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="数据库配置.png"></p><blockquote><p>添加对mapper的扫描 加在启动类上</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/19390595-fa5171857abe9ef3.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/800" alt="scanner.png"></p><blockquote><p>新建表 添加对应实体 并添加对应mapper 继承tk包中的mapper</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/19390595-5a75090dbcceec9d.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/800" alt="表名字段名.png"></p><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/19390595-10503c6e8b551ca8.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/800" alt="对应查询mapper.png"></p><blockquote><p>测试使用 注入接口 调用方法</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/19390595-1ed5f947809af7d9.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/800" alt="添加访问.png"></p><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/19390595-2259e73495e30e99.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/800" alt="前端展示查询结果.png"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
